=\"string\">&quot;正在调用func2()!&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">dicswi = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">&#x27;key0&#x27;</span> : func0,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">&#x27;key1&#x27;</span> : func1,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">&#x27;key2&#x27;</span> : func2</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">dicswi[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;key0&#x27;</span>]()</span><br><span class=\"line\">dicswi[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;key1&#x27;</span>]()</span><br><span class=\"line\">dicswi[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;key2&#x27;</span>]()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>......</code></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Django","link":"2020/09/08/Django"},"next":{"title":"函数装饰器与闭包","link":"2020/06/25/函数装饰器与闭包"},"plink":"https://user-hrsat.github.io/2020/06/29/Python小技巧/","toc":[{"id":"python小技巧","title":"Python小技巧","index":"1","children":[{"id":"其一","title":"其一","index":"1.1"}]}],"copyright":{"author":"User-Hrsat","link":"<a href=\"https://user-hrsat.github.io/2020/06/29/Python小技巧/\" title=\"Python小技巧\">https://user-hrsat.github.io/2020/06/29/Python小技巧/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/deed.zh\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"2020年6月29日"}}